</div><div class="wall_post_text">Сибирь-матушка<br><br>Сибирь в легендах и фотографиях<br><br>Ещё в XVII веке Сибирь (Сибирская украйна) охватывала дальневосточные и уральские земли. Сегодня – это территория от Урала до Охотского моря и от Монголии и казахских степей до самого Северного Ледовитого океана...</div><div class="page_post_sized_thumbs  clear_fix" style="width: 496px; height: 342px;"><a  onclick="return showPhoto('-41109373_302394302', 'wall-41240732_1254', {&quot;temp&quot;:{&quot;base&quot;:&quot;https://pp.userapi.com/c412123/v412123329/&quot;,&quot;x_&quot;:[&quot;4ab/xcC96FE1llA&quot;,604,340],&quot;y_&quot;:[&quot;4ac/aoN5sCcO9Uw&quot;,807,454],&quot;z_&quot;:[&quot;4ad/KX4kKdsGzr4&quot;,1000,563]},queue:1}, event)" style="width: 496px; height: 227px; background-image: url(https://pp.userapi.com/c412123/v412123329/4b1/bdv7Jb-CnVY.jpg)" class="page_post_thumb_wrap image_cover  page_post_thumb_last_column fl_l"></a><a  onclick="return showPhoto('-41109373_302394303', 'wall-41240732_1254', {&quot;temp&quot;:{&quot;base&quot;:&quot;https://pp.userapi.com/c412123/v412123329/&quot;,&quot;x_&quot;:[&quot;4b4/aXwQHfnlvRY&quot;,604,453],&quot;y_&quot;:[&quot;4b5/SoRO6wnc1e4&quot;,807,605],&quot;z_&quot;:[&quot;4b6/73ZHMNYr__U&quot;,1024,768]},queue:1}, event)" style="width: 146px; height: 109px; background-image: url(https://pp.userapi.com/c412123/v412123329/4b8/sn5htFEbUsU.jpg)" class="page_post_thumb_wrap image_cover  page_post_thumb_last_row fl_l"></a><a  onclick="return showPhoto('-41109373_302394304', 'wall-41240732_1254', {&quot;temp&quot;:{&quot;base&quot;:&quot;https://pp.userapi.com/c412123/v412123329/&quot;,&quot;x_&quot;:[&quot;4bd/fZu7Aamzdos&quot;,604,402],&quot;y_&quot;:[&quot;4be/cgti5yoh75E&quot;,807,537],&quot;z_&quot;:[&quot;4bf/MixqWSUk-5E&quot;,1200,798]},queue:1}, event)" style="width: 164px; height: 109px; background-image: url(https://pp.userapi.com/c412123/v412123329/4c1/AuRIIbw_FX0.jpg)" class="page_post_thumb_wrap image_cover  page