      <h5 class="copy_post_author"><a class="copy_author" data-post-id="-41109373_111722" data-parent-post-id="-41240732_1253" href="/slavyanskie_korni">&#10004; СЛАВЯНСКИЕ ТРАДИЦИИ</a> </h5>
      <div class="copy_post_date"><a class="published_by_date"  class="post_link"  href="/wall-41109373_111722"  onclick="return showWiki({w: 'wall-41109373_111722'}, false, event);" >17 апр 2013 в 22:00</a></div>
